Lister is the worst lecturer I've had in all academia. Never felt a need to write a RateMyProf until now. He throws hundreds of pages of readings each week with little guidance. 

DO NOT TAKE HIS COURSE. Talk to any 3L and everyone has experienced, or heard a Lister horror story. Most get bad grades, yet even high grade earners agree he is awful.
